@NODE "History" "History"

@{code}@{jcenter}@{apen 2}History
@{jleft}@{apen 1}
Here is what has changed since MWB_Stuff5.1:

· The guide (as usual) has been completely revamped.
· Added a @{"Photogenics drawer" LINK "ID"}.
· Removed @{"MagicWB-Demon" LINK "Sorry"}, Compare.anim, MUI_Preview.pic, 18&Older.lha.
· Added @{"MUI_Template" SYSTEM "sys:utilities/multiview misc/MUI_Template"} and updated @{"MWB_Template" SYSTEM "sys:utilities/multiview misc/MWB_Template"}.
· Added more @{"Big_Patterns" LINK "BP"}: @{"Courtney4.iff" SYSTEM "sys:utilities/multiview Patterns/big_patterns/Courtney4.iff"}, @{"KathyFlag.iff" SYSTEM "sys:utilities/multiview Patterns/big_patterns/KathyFlag.iff"}, & @{"MädchenAmick.iff" SYSTEM "sys:utilities/multiview Patterns/big_patterns/MädchenAmick.iff"}.
· Added more @{"Sml_Patterns" LINK "SP"}: @{"XFiles.iff" SYSTEM "sys:utilities/multiview Patterns/sml_patterns/XFiles.iff"}, @{"XFiles2.iff" SYSTEM "sys:utilities/multiview Patterns/sml_patterns/XFiles2.iff"}, & @{"XFiles_MagicCopper.iff" SYSTEM "sys:utilities/multiview Patterns/sml_patterns/XFiles_MagicCopper.iff"}.
· Added more @{"Win_Patterns" LINK "WP"}: @{"ColoredStones.iff" SYSTEM "sys:utilities/multiview Patterns/win_patterns/ColoredStones.iff"}, @{"FlagStone.iff" SYSTEM "sys:utilities/multiview Patterns/win_patterns/FlagStone.iff"}, & @{"Mush.iff" SYSTEM "sys:utilities/multiview Patterns/win_patterns/Mush.iff"}.
· Included a new grab of my @{"DOpusbench" SYSTEM "sys:utilities/multiview TrevsDB.iff"}.

Here is what has been added since MWB_Stuff5:

· The guide file has undergone a complete overhaul.
· Added some @{"MUI gadgets" LINK "MUIDrawer"}.
· Included a MUI_Preview.pic.
· Put in a new @{"Disk Icon" LINK "8"}, some @{"Enlan Icons" LINK "Enlan"} and an @{"MCP Drawer Icon" LINK "ID"}.
· Added 3 new @{"WinPatterns" LINK "WP"} and a bunch of new @{"SmallPatterns" LINK "SP"}.

Man! It doesn't look like much when I list it out like this, but trust me, it
took a hell of a lot of time!

